1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,200
Here's what science actually says about insulin resistance.

2
00:00:03,200 --> 00:00:07,600
Insulin resistance is when your cells stop responding to insulin effectively.

3
00:00:07,600 --> 00:00:10,400
This can lead to high blood sugar.

4
00:00:10,400 --> 00:00:12,800
But it’s not just about sugar.

5
00:00:12,800 --> 00:00:16,800
It can affect your energy, mood, and even weight gain.

6
00:00:16,800 --> 00:00:20,400
Studies show that lifestyle changes can improve insulin sensitivity.

7
00:00:20,400 --> 00:00:22,400
Exercise and diet are key.

8
00:00:22,400 --> 00:00:26,400
Understanding this can help you take control of your health.

9
00:00:26,400 --> 00:00:29,200
Are you ready to make a change?

10
00:00:29,200 --> 00:00:31,600
Follow for more science-backed health insights!
